                                        159
                                    ],
                                    "score": 1.0,
                                    "content": "The use of ACEi and ARB treatment has been associated with an increased risk of adverse effects to the fetus during pregnancy. Women who are planning for pregnancy or who are pregnant while on RAS blockade treatment should have the drug discontinued (see Practice Point 1.2.4).",
                                    "type": "text"
